# Next.js App Rules

- These apps use Next.js 15 App Router and React 19.
- Reuse shared UI components and import shared styles where needed.
- Keep styling aligned to the design system with CSS variables.
- Prefer the shared page shell pattern: `.page-container`, `.page-header`, `.page-content`.
- Use shared auth session primitives when auth-aware UI is needed.
- Keep app-specific logic in the app, and shared logic in `packages/`.
